      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "rationale": "Simulated hemolysis index compared quantitatively against experimental measurements at all 5 operating points using normalised RMS error and area metric. Mean normalised error 14.2%, within the 15% acceptance criterion. Uncertainty intervals overlap at 4 of 5 operating points.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
